击，这将导致原油市场的风险溢价再次上升。周一，据新华社，伊朗表示不会放弃回应以色列“侵略”的权利。","display_time":1730151451,"id":3732056,"image":{"uri":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/4f1bba70-fb9b-45f6-aa2e-520e93e13495.jpeg","height":178,"width":284,"size":6878},"is_in_vip_privilege":false,"is_priced":false,"limited_time":0,"source_name":"何浩","source_uri":"","subtitle":"","title":"美油暴跌超6%，两年多最惨，花旗下调油价目标，但也有人警告伊朗或反击","uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/articles/3732056"},{"author":{"avatar":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/08507e99-88ee-4368-b332-c44def86720c","display_name":"赵颖","id":120000004514},"content_short":"日本央行官员们认为，物价大幅超过央行7月份季度预测的风险很小，因此无需迅速采取行动。在采取下一步行动之前，有必要监测美国经济以及下个月美国大选对经济和市场的潜在影响以及其他高度不确定因素。","display_time":1729258560,"id":3730880,"image":{"uri":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/275f6049-3ad6-4396-a360-b13e811ee03b.jpeg","height":435,"width":650,"size":234263},"is_in_vip_privilege":false,"is_priced":false,"limited_time":0,"source_name":"","source_uri":"","subtitle":"","title":"报道：日本央行官员称10月不急于加息，也没有必要调整通胀预期","uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/articles/3730880"},{"author":{"avatar":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/a4ceed30-ef97-4546-b874-6ca5e3d254e3","display_name":"黄雯雯","id":120000004778},"content_short":"“特朗普交易”的新变化在于美股科技股更有韧性、能源股表现更弱、美债利率不升反降、黄金表现更强等。平安证券认为，目前选情仍然胶着，“特朗普交易”能走多远较不确定。","display_time":1729238996,"id":3730764,"image":{"uri":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/2bda1410-b3ba-4992-a401-352058cc1ecc.jpeg","height":528,"width":792,"size":98344},"is_in_vip_privilege":false,"is_priced":false,"limited_time":0,"source_name":"","source_uri":"","subtitle":"","title":"“特朗普交易”重启，有何不同？","uri":"https://wallstreetcn.com/articles/3730764"},{"author":{"avatar":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/bf080e69-1f3f-45d5-8bb4-4b9dc207789e","display_name":"王小娟","id":120000004768},"content_short":"家家都想要爆款。","display_time":1729088950,"id":3730582,"image":{"uri":"https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/4ecc39b2-d024-4587-945a-d4e367827ac1.jpeg","height":788,"width":1024,"size":102208},"is_in_vip_privilege":false,"is_priced":false,"limited_time":0,"